152
00:08:24,780 --> 00:08:28,820
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">ma non dovresti sottovalutare Sham dei Miaoban Brothers!</font>

153
00:08:32,990 --> 00:08:37,200
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Hai perso qualcosa?
Io non ne so niente nel caso.</font>

154
00:08:37,910 --> 00:08:38,910
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Eccolo...</font>

155
00:08:38,910 --> 00:08:40,370
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><font size="72">Nota: "Nekobaba" è un modo di dire "rubare", 
qui è un gioco di parole con "neko", cioè gatto.</font></font>

156
00:08:38,910 --> 00:08:40,370
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Il "Gatto Ladro"...</font>

157
00:08:40,790 --> 00:08:42,880
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Ridammi quella spada!</font>

158
00:08:42,880 --> 00:08:47,300
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Ridartela? 
Se vuoi una spada, ne hai già una, no?</font>

159
00:08:50,340 --> 00:08:52,470
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Queste sono d'intralcio.</font>

160
00:08:59,270 --> 00:09:00,560
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Bene!</font>

161
00:09:00,560 --> 00:09:02,650
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Così sono più leggero!</font>

162
00:09:02,650 --> 00:09:06,320
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Dovresti trattare bene... le cose degli altri!</font>

163
00:09:10,400 --> 00:09:12,160
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Bastardo! </font>

164
00:09:14,280 --> 00:09:14,950
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Cosa?!</font>

165
00:09:16,160 --> 00:09:17,950
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Cosa avresti tagliato?!</font>

166
00:09:17,950 --> 00:09:19,960
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><font size="72">Nota: "Nekoze" significa "gobbo", 
qui è un gioco di parole con "neko", cioè gatto.</font></font>

167
00:09:17,950 --> 00:09:19,960
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Sono gobbo come un gatto!</font>

168
00:09:22,710 --> 00:09:24,420
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Fallo, Buchi!</font>

169
00:09:24,420 --> 00:09:25,340
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">È il tuo turno!</font>

170
00:09:25,340 --> 00:09:27,210
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Certo, Sham!</font>

171
00:09:27,920 --> 00:09:30,220
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Pestone...</font>

172
00:09:32,890 --> 00:09:34,720
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">del gatto!</font>

173
00:09:36,890 --> 00:09:38,520
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Maledizione!</font>

174
00:09:38,520 --> 00:09:39,850
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">È riuscito a sfuggirmi?!</font>

175
00:09:39,850 --> 00:09:42,600
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Ehi! Tienilo come si deve, Sham!</font>

176
00:09:42,600 --> 00:09:43,980
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Scusa, scusa.</font>

177
00:09:43,980 --> 00:09:47,020
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Quel bastardo è più forte di quel che pensavo!</font>

178
00:09:47,780 --> 00:09:49,530
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Non scherziamo...</font>

179
00:09:49,530 --> 00:09:54,200
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Con un solo colpo di quelli...
tutte le mie ossa verrebbero polverizzate!</font>

180
00:09:54,950 --> 00:09:56,830
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Questa volta non ci sfuggirai!</font>

181
00:09:56,830 --> 00:09:58,120
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Certamente!</font>

182
00:09:58,620 --> 00:10:01,750
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Lo stile a una spada non è il mio forte, ma...</font>

183
00:10:02,790 --> 00:10:04,750
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Andiamo, Buchi!</font>

184
00:10:05,170 --> 00:10:06,960
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Ci siamo, Sham!</font>

185
00:10:06,960 --> 00:10:10,670
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">– Grande Marcia del Salice Felino!
– Grande Marcia del Salice Felino!</font>

186
00:10:18,100 --> 00:10:20,560
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Oh no! Stanno avendo la meglio su Zoro!</font>

187
00:10:23,810 --> 00:10:25,310
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Che vuoi fare?!</font>

188
00:10:25,310 --> 00:10:29,070
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Non ne uscirà vivo se continuerà ad essere 
attaccato da due persone insieme!</font>

189
00:10:29,070 --> 00:10:30,650
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Gli darò una mano!</font>

190
00:10:30,650 --> 00:10:32,280
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Prendete questo...</font>

191
00:10:32,280 --> 00:10:33,490
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Stella di Piombo!</font>

192
00:10:39,700 --> 00:10:40,870
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Un'apertura!</font>

193
00:10:46,880 --> 00:10:49,880
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Perché diavolo attacchi un alleato?!</font>

194
00:10:50,630 --> 00:10:52,090
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">No, ti sbagli!</font>

195
00:10:52,090 --> 00:10:55,630
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Lui... sembra che si sia 
fatto colpire di proposito.</font>

196
00:10:55,630 --> 00:10:57,510
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Eh? Di proposito?!</font>

197
00:10:59,560 --> 00:11:01,560
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Usopp, sei un idiota!</font>

198
00:11:01,560 --> 00:11:02,770
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Vuoi morire?!</font>

199
00:11:07,270 --> 00:11:08,980
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Può essere che...</font>

200
00:11:09,480 --> 00:11:11,980
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">siamo stati <i>noi</i> a essere salvati?</font>

201
00:11:11,980 --> 00:11:15,990
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Se li avessi colpiti con la fionda, quei due probabilmente...</font>

202
00:11:15,990 --> 00:11:19,120
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">sarebbero venuti ad attaccare noi.</font>

203
00:11:19,780 --> 00:11:20,990
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Lui...</font>

204
00:11:21,540 --> 00:11:23,750
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">anche se non doveva farlo...!</font>

205
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:28,290
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Dannazione!</font>

206
00:11:28,290 --> 00:11:31,630
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Se avessi almeno un'altra spada...!</font>

207
00:11:33,880 --> 00:11:35,670
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Vado a prendere le spade!</font>

208
00:11:35,670 --> 00:11:37,760
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Se le darò a Zoro, vincerà di sicuro!</font>

209
00:11:37,760 --> 00:11:39,220
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Vado io allora...!</font>

210
00:11:40,100 --> 00:11:41,600
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Non sforzarti troppo.</font>

211
00:11:41,600 --> 00:11:43,430
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Riesci a malapena a stare in piedi!</font>

212
00:11:45,180 --> 00:11:46,140
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Ehi, Nami!</font>

213
00:12:06,330 --> 00:12:07,370
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Nami!</font>

214
00:12:07,710 --> 00:12:10,000
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Cosa vuoi da queste spade?</font>

215
00:12:24,970 --> 00:12:29,230
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">No, ecco...
Ci sono state delle complicazioni...</font>

216
00:12:33,150 --> 00:12:37,240
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">L'alba è passata ormai da un bel po'...</font>

217
00:12:37,240 --> 00:12:41,620
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">e stavo giusto pensando che il piano non
 stesse procedendo come da programma...</font>

218
00:12:42,160 --> 00:12:44,490
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">C-Captain Kuro!</font>

219
00:12:44,490 --> 00:12:46,120
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">C-Ci ucciderà!</font>

220
00:12:52,580 --> 00:12:54,040
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">È un disastro...</font>

221
00:13:07,890 --> 00:13:11,520
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Che diavolo è tutto questo?!</font>

222
00:13:14,230 --> 00:13:18,070
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Pensare che dei mocciosi del 
genere sono riusciti a fermarvi...</font>

223
00:13:18,690 --> 00:13:21,660
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">I Pirati del Gatto Nero 
sono proprio caduti in basso.</font>

224
00:13:22,490 --> 00:13:23,740
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Vero...</font>

225
00:13:24,620 --> 00:13:26,200
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Jango?!</font>

226
00:13:30,500 --> 00:13:33,630
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">P-P-Però...</font>

227
00:13:34,710 --> 00:13:39,210
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Q-Quel moccioso che avevi detto 
che non avrebbe causato problemi...</font>

228
00:13:42,300 --> 00:13:44,140
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Sì, l'ho detto.</font>

229
00:13:44,140 --> 00:13:45,220
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Eh?</font>

230
00:13:45,600 --> 00:13:47,810
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">E quindi?</font>

231
00:13:47,810 --> 00:13:52,730
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Sapevo che avrebbe provato ad affrontarci.</font>

232
00:13:52,730 --> 00:13:55,480
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">L'unica cosa che non avevo previsto...</font>

233
00:13:55,480 --> 00:13:58,610
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">è la vostra debolezza!</font>

234
00:13:58,610 --> 00:14:01,490
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Noi... deboli?</font>

235
00:14:01,490 --> 00:14:03,740
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">C-Chi sarebbe un debole?!</font>

236
00:14:03,740 --> 00:14:05,410
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Cosa dici, Captain Kuro?!</font>

237
00:14:08,200 --> 00:14:10,450
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">In effetti, tu eri forte!</font>

238
00:14:10,950 --> 00:14:13,210
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Ma questo era tre anni fa!</font>

239
00:14:13,210 --> 00:14:18,130
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Mentre tu eri in quel villaggio a prendertela 
comoda, noi non siamo stati mica a oziare!</font>

240
00:14:18,130 --> 00:14:19,590
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Esatto!</font>

241
00:14:19,590 --> 00:14:24,050
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Abbiamo attaccato diversi villaggi e affondato diverse ciurme di pirati!</font>

242
00:14:26,010 --> 00:14:27,810
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Cosa vorreste dire?</font>

243
00:14:28,720 --> 00:14:31,730
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Con tre anni di vuoto...</font>

244
00:14:31,730 --> 00:14:35,100
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">non puoi battere gli attuali Miaoban Brothers!</font>

245
00:14:39,190 --> 00:14:42,150
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Fermatevi, Buchi, Sham!</font>

246
00:14:47,990 --> 00:14:50,490
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Tu non sei più il nostro capitano!</font>

247
00:14:50,490 --> 00:14:53,410
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Perdonaci, ma ti faremo fuori!</font>

248
00:15:05,930 --> 00:15:08,350
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Q-Quando è arrivato dietro di loro?!</font>

249
00:15:08,930 --> 00:15:10,560
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">E quelle armi...</font>

250
00:15:12,470 --> 00:15:14,730
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Chi è che vorreste far fuori?</font>

251
00:15:15,980 --> 00:15:17,940
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">– Ci ha...
– aggirati?!</font>

252
00:15:22,030 --> 00:15:24,070
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Eh?! Non c'è più!</font>

253
00:15:28,780 --> 00:15:31,120
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Eccolo... il "Passo Furtivo".</font>

254
00:15:35,960 --> 00:15:38,040
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Proprio come dite...</font>

255
00:15:42,750 --> 00:15:46,220
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Mi sento ancora un po' intorpidito.</font>

256
00:15:47,030 --> 00:15:48,590
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Li tratta come dei bambini</font>

257
00:15:48,590 --> 00:15:52,220
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">nonostante prima tenessero testa
 a Zoro, anche se con una spada sola.</font>

258
00:15:53,470 --> 00:15:57,810
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Il "Passo Furtivo" di quell'uomo è una tecnica di movimento silenziosa.</font>

259
00:15:58,560 --> 00:16:03,440
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Anche contro cinquanta assassini, verrebbero tutti
uccisi prima di accorgersi della sua presenza!</font>

260
00:16:04,650 --> 00:16:08,660
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Noi... non riusciremo mai a fuggire dal suo piano!</font>

261
00:16:09,530 --> 00:16:15,370
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Inoltre, incontrarlo dopo tre anni e
 vedere quell'abitudine, mi ha fatto venire i brividi.</font>

262
00:16:16,000 --> 00:16:21,960
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Un modo bizzarro di alzarsi gli 
occhiali quando ha le unghie da gatto</font>

263
00:16:21,960 --> 00:16:24,760
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">per evitare di graffiarsi il viso.</font>

264
00:16:33,060 --> 00:16:36,230
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Sembra che anch'io sia diventato più mite</font>

265
00:16:36,730 --> 00:16:40,310
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">dopo tre anni fermo su quella collina.</font>

266
00:16:42,230 --> 00:16:44,320
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Vi do cinque minuti.</font>

267
00:16:46,440 --> 00:16:50,240
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Se in cinque minuti non riuscirete a sistemare questa situazione...</font>

268
00:16:52,240 --> 00:16:54,990
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">vi ucciderò tutti con le mie mani,</font>

269
00:16:55,740 --> 00:16:58,410
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">nessuno escluso!</font>

270
00:17:07,590 --> 00:17:08,470
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">C-Cinque minuti...</font>

271
00:17:09,220 --> 00:17:10,800
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Cinque minuti ci basteranno!</font>

272
00:17:11,760 --> 00:17:13,470
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Ah! Lui!</font>

273
00:17:13,470 --> 00:17:18,560
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Se riuscissimo a sconfiggerlo, 
potremmo attraversare questa pendenza!</font>

274
00:17:26,650 --> 00:17:29,070
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">È quello che stavamo sconfiggendo prima!</font>

275
00:17:29,070 --> 00:17:31,200
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Lo faremo a pezzi in cinque secondi!</font>

276
00:17:31,700 --> 00:17:35,410
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Conto su di voi, Miaoban Brothers!</font>

277
00:17:38,330 --> 00:17:39,200
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Zoro!</font>

278
00:17:43,670 --> 00:17:44,630
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Cosa?!</font>

279
00:17:44,630 --> 00:17:46,090
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">C-Cretina!</font>

280
00:17:46,090 --> 00:17:48,630
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Hai preso a calci le mie spade?!</font>

281
00:17:49,590 --> 00:17:51,050
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">E il "grazie" dov'è?</font>

282
00:17:52,300 --> 00:17:53,140
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Giusto.</font>

283
00:17:54,640 --> 00:17:56,260
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Grazie!</font>

284
00:17:58,770 --> 00:18:00,020
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">È inutile!</font>

285
00:18:00,020 --> 00:18:01,520
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Anche usando tre spade,</font>

286
00:18:01,520 --> 00:18:03,310
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">la tua forza rimane quella!</font>

287
00:18:05,360 --> 00:18:13,820
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82"><font size="72">Nota: Gioco di parole tra  "tora gari" (caccia alla tigre) 
e il taglio di capelli alla moicana Toragari. </font></font>

288
00:18:05,360 --> 00:18:06,060
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Tora...</font>

289
00:18:09,610 --> 00:18:11,530
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Non vi è chiaro, eh?</font>

290
00:18:12,280 --> 00:18:13,820
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Gari!</font>

291
00:18:18,580 --> 00:18:21,160
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Ancora... quattro minuti.</font>

292
00:18:24,170 --> 00:18:27,960
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">C'è differenza tra il saper usare tre spade</font>

293
00:18:27,960 --> 00:18:29,960
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">e il saper usare lo Stile a Tre Spade.</font>

294
00:18:35,680 --> 00:18:36,550
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Wow...</font>

295
00:18:39,810 --> 00:18:41,270
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Che potenza...</font>

296
00:18:45,560 --> 00:18:47,150
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Con un solo colpo...</font>

297
00:18:55,910 --> 00:18:59,280
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Ha sconfitto i Miaoban 
Brothers con un solo colpo...</font>

298
00:19:10,460 --> 00:19:12,010
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Non preoccuparti!</font>

299
00:19:12,920 --> 00:19:19,510
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Anche senza aspettare cinque minuti, vi farò fuori tutti io, nessuno escluso.</font>

300
00:19:33,820 --> 00:19:36,570
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Ancora... tre minuti.</font>

301
00:19:40,370 --> 00:19:44,250
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">L-Lui... lo ammazzerò.</font>

302
00:19:47,540 --> 00:19:49,670
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Capitano!</font>

303
00:19:49,670 --> 00:19:52,840
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">M-Mi ipnotizzi...</font>

304
00:19:54,840 --> 00:19:57,300
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">T-Ti prego, capitano!</font>

305
00:19:57,840 --> 00:19:59,430
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">È vivo.</font>

306
00:19:59,430 --> 00:20:01,010
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Sei stato superficiale.</font>

307
00:20:03,890 --> 00:20:06,850
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Si è salvato per via del suo grasso resistente?</font>

308
00:20:28,370 --> 00:20:30,580
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Fallo! Buchi!</font>

309
00:20:35,050 --> 00:20:38,260
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Tsk! Ancora l'ipnosi?</font>

310
00:20:42,010 --> 00:20:43,260
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Quel tipo è pericoloso.</font>

311
00:20:43,760 --> 00:20:46,730
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">È già stato capace di crepare da solo il terreno.</font>

312
00:20:49,350 --> 00:20:51,860
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Cosa potrà succedere 
dopo il suo potenziamento?!</font>

313
00:21:00,990 --> 00:21:02,450
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">È la mia occasione!</font>

314
00:21:02,450 --> 00:21:05,910
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Devo svegliarlo finché posso!</font>

315
00:21:05,910 --> 00:21:08,540
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">E adesso cosa vuoi fare?</font>

316
00:21:09,580 --> 00:21:11,290
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Che donna subdola...</font>

317
00:21:11,710 --> 00:21:14,920
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Anche se tutti siamo gravemente feriti, lui...!</font>

318
00:21:16,300 --> 00:21:17,630
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Muori!</font>

319
00:21:21,680 --> 00:21:23,220
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Svegliati!</font>

320
00:21:23,220 --> 00:21:25,100
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Nami! Attenta!</font>

321
00:21:29,560 --> 00:21:31,060
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Tagliati in due!</font>

322
00:21:32,440 --> 00:21:33,690
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Schivalo!</font>

323
00:21:35,360 --> 00:21:37,650
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">C-Cosa?!</font>

324
00:21:38,650 --> 00:21:40,070
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">È un chakram!</font>

325
00:21:40,070 --> 00:21:42,530
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Non era solo uno strumento per l'ipnosi?!</font>

326
00:21:43,740 --> 00:21:48,580
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Nami! Come hai potuto calpestarmi la faccia?!</font>

327
00:21:50,370 --> 00:21:51,920
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Q-Quel tizio è ancora vivo?!</font>

328
00:21:53,080 --> 00:21:56,920
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Chissà se ha avuto un pessimo tempismo
o se è semplicemente una brava persona...</font>

329
00:22:01,220 --> 00:22:02,380
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">L-Luffy?</font>

330
00:22:07,810 --> 00:22:09,350
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Luffy!</font>

331
00:22:09,350 --> 00:22:12,270
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Ahia...</font>

332
00:22:12,640 --> 00:22:15,020
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Ahia!</font>

333
00:22:15,440 --> 00:22:17,900
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">È-È resuscitato!</font>

334
00:22:17,900 --> 00:22:19,730
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Che guaio... di questo passo...!</font>

335
00:22:19,730 --> 00:22:22,400
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">In cinque minuti è assolutamente impossibile!</font>

336
00:22:23,320 --> 00:22:26,490
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Nami! Fa male, bastarda!</font>

337
00:22:26,490 --> 00:22:28,450
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Non sono stata mica io!</font>

338
00:22:28,450 --> 00:22:30,000
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">N-Non sono...</font>

339
00:22:33,460 --> 00:22:34,790
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">N-Nami?</font>

340
00:22:34,790 --> 00:22:37,210
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Ti... sei ferita alla spalla?</font>

341
00:22:38,250 --> 00:22:40,670
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Non è niente, sto bene.</font>

342
00:22:40,670 --> 00:22:44,130
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">In ogni caso, ho fatto tutto quello che potevo.</font>

343
00:22:44,130 --> 00:22:46,430
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Posso lasciare il resto a te, vero?</font>

344
00:22:47,470 --> 00:22:51,560
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Non possiamo assolutamente 
perdere questo combattimento, no?</font>

345
00:22:51,560 --> 00:22:52,350
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Già.</font>

346
00:22:53,640 --> 00:22:57,020
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Fai del tuo meglio! 
Fallo per il mio tesoro!</font>

347
00:22:57,020 --> 00:23:00,230
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Bene! Così ti riconosco!</font>

348
00:23:01,440 --> 00:23:03,780
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Ancora... un minuto.</font>

349
00:23:06,110 --> 00:23:07,910
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Non può essere!</font>

350
00:23:07,910 --> 00:23:10,330
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Anche il capitano Jango e Buchi</font>

351
00:23:10,660 --> 00:23:14,160
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">non riusciranno mai a 
finirli in un solo minuto!</font>

352
00:23:24,510 --> 00:23:27,340
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Buchi! Non c'è tempo per pensare!</font>

353
00:23:28,090 --> 00:23:30,310
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Tu fai fuori quel bastardo con l'haramaki!</font>

354
00:23:30,310 --> 00:23:34,520
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">E io... mi occuperò di 
quello strano moccioso,</font>

355
00:23:41,070 --> 00:23:42,860
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">quel tipo dal cappello di paglia!</font>

356
00:23:45,450 --> 00:23:48,370
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Ma come? È arrivato anche il maggiordomo cattivo?</font>

357
00:23:49,320 --> 00:23:51,030
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Lui...</font>

358
00:23:51,030 --> 00:23:53,750
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">È caduto dalla scogliera, dovrebbe essere morto.</font>

359
00:23:55,500 --> 00:23:56,790
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Beh, non importa.</font>

360
00:24:09,260 --> 00:24:10,850
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Non avvicinarti...</font>

361
00:24:14,310 --> 00:24:16,430
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">alle mie spalle!</font>

362
00:24:17,270 --> 00:24:19,230
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Kaya!</font>

363
00:24:36,200 --> 00:24:38,120
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Usopp, stai bene?</font>

364
00:24:38,120 --> 00:24:39,460
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">K-Kaya...</font>

365
00:24:39,460 --> 00:24:41,130
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Cosa sei venuta a fare qui?!</font>

366
00:24:41,840 --> 00:24:44,090
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Scusami, Usopp.</font>

367
00:24:44,090 --> 00:24:46,920
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">So che anche scusandomi, non potrai mai perdonarmi,</font>

368
00:24:46,920 --> 00:24:49,300
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">ma non riuscivo proprio a credere</font>

369
00:24:49,300 --> 00:24:52,220
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">c-che Klahadore fosse un pirata.</font>

370
00:24:52,220 --> 00:24:54,180
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Non importa!</font>

371
00:24:54,180 --> 00:24:55,640
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Perché sei venuta qui?</font>

372
00:24:55,640 --> 00:24:57,680
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Ti avevo detto di scappare!</font>

373
00:24:57,680 --> 00:24:59,890
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Sta cercando di ucciderti!</font>

374
00:24:59,890 --> 00:25:03,730
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Ma...! Tu stai ancora combattendo!</font>

375
00:25:05,230 --> 00:25:09,030
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Anche... dopo che ti ho trattato così male.</font>

376
00:25:09,030 --> 00:25:12,240
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Stai combattendo anche se sei pieno di ferite!</font>

377
00:25:12,240 --> 00:25:13,030
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Per questo, io...</font>

378
00:25:13,030 --> 00:25:14,620
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Signorina Kaya.</font>

379
00:25:15,700 --> 00:25:18,160
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Perché... è qui?</font>

380
00:25:20,830 --> 00:25:23,590
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Ora... b-basta.</font>

381
00:25:26,760 --> 00:25:30,260
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Devi fermarti, Klahadore!</font>

382
00:25:36,680 --> 00:25:39,640
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Merry... mi ha raccontato tutto.</font>

383
00:25:42,480 --> 00:25:44,810
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Quella è la ragazza della villa, no?</font>

384
00:25:45,270 --> 00:25:48,150
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Ma quindi... quella ragazza è 
l'obiettivo finale del piano!</font>

385
00:25:48,150 --> 00:25:50,900
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Allora non serve più andare al villaggio?</font>

386
00:25:50,900 --> 00:25:53,110
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Basterà far fuori quella donna, no?</font>

387
00:25:56,240 --> 00:25:57,990
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Klahadore, per favore!</font>

388
00:25:57,990 --> 00:26:01,460
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Se vuoi il mio patrimonio, te lo darò tutto, però...</font>

389
00:26:01,460 --> 00:26:03,250
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Vattene da questo villaggio!</font>

390
00:26:03,250 --> 00:26:04,880
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Immediatamente!</font>

391
00:26:04,880 --> 00:26:09,090
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Lo accetterò con gratitudine, ma...</font>

392
00:26:09,590 --> 00:26:14,220
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">C'è un'altra cosa che voglio.</font>

393
00:26:16,180 --> 00:26:18,770
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Ciò che voglio è...</font>

394
00:26:20,310 --> 00:26:22,640
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">la pace interiore.</font>

395
00:26:23,140 --> 00:26:24,850
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Pace interiore?</font>

396
00:26:25,610 --> 00:26:29,320
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Esatto. 
Voglio semplicemente la pace interiore.</font>

397
00:26:30,530 --> 00:26:34,530
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">La fiducia degli abitanti del villaggio che ho coltivato in questi tre anni</font>

398
00:26:34,530 --> 00:26:39,790
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">è diventata fonte per me di risate e conforto.</font>

399
00:26:39,790 --> 00:26:46,330
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">È per questo che... voglio avere 
questa pace interiore per sempre.</font>

400
00:26:53,340 --> 00:26:55,050
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Quindi...</font>

401
00:26:55,800 --> 00:26:59,180
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Quindi me la prenderò con 
la forza quella pace interiore!</font>

402
00:26:59,180 --> 00:27:01,640
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Insieme al tuo patrimonio.</font>

403
00:27:02,270 --> 00:27:04,600
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">In pratica, i pirati giungeranno al villaggio!</font>

404
00:27:07,730 --> 00:27:08,650
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">E poi...!</font>

405
00:27:09,230 --> 00:27:12,360
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">tu morirai lasciando un testamento!</font>

406
00:27:12,740 --> 00:27:16,160
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Queste due cose sono inevitabili!</font>

407
00:27:16,740 --> 00:27:18,660
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">N-No...</font>

408
00:27:19,660 --> 00:27:21,870
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">N-Non sei Klahadore...</font>

409
00:27:22,540 --> 00:27:26,370
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Scappa! Devi scappare, Kaya! Qualsiasi cosa dirai, è inutile!</font>

410
00:27:26,370 --> 00:27:27,750
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Scappa!</font>

411
00:27:27,750 --> 00:27:30,710
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">N-Non sei Klahadore...</font>

412
00:27:30,710 --> 00:27:32,960
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Tu non sei...!</font>

413
00:27:34,170 --> 00:27:35,680
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Kaya...</font>

414
00:27:36,090 --> 00:27:37,510
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Vattene!</font>

415
00:27:37,510 --> 00:27:38,930
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Va' via da questo villaggio!</font>

416
00:27:39,260 --> 00:27:40,890
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Capisco.</font>

417
00:27:40,890 --> 00:27:44,850
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">In questi tre anni, anche tu sei diventata ammirevole.</font>

418
00:27:45,730 --> 00:27:47,690
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Signorina Kaya...</font>

419
00:27:48,860 --> 00:27:51,190
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Si ricorda?</font>

420
00:27:51,190 --> 00:27:54,280
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">In tre anni, sono successe molte cose...</font>

421
00:27:55,320 --> 00:27:59,530
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Ancor prima che perdesse i 
suoi genitori e si ammalasse...</font>

422
00:27:59,530 --> 00:28:03,410
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">abbiamo passato molto tempo insieme.</font>

423
00:28:04,500 --> 00:28:06,000
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Mi vengono in mente...</font>

424
00:28:09,710 --> 00:28:11,130
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">tante cose.</font>

425
00:28:11,130 --> 00:28:15,760
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Quei momenti in cui abbiamo 
sofferto e abbiamo gioito insieme...</font>

426
00:28:16,260 --> 00:28:18,760
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">K-Klahadore...</font>

427
00:28:19,760 --> 00:28:21,760
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Quando siamo usciti in città...</font>

428
00:28:22,510 --> 00:28:25,270
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Quando le è venuta la febbre e mi sono preso cura di lei...</font>

429
00:28:26,270 --> 00:28:30,270
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Quando ascoltavi le mie storie allegramente...</font>

430
00:28:32,360 --> 00:28:35,440
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Ho dedicato la mia vita a lei.</font>

431
00:28:36,650 --> 00:28:38,450
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Sempre...</font>

432
00:28:38,450 --> 00:28:40,660
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Sì, sempre...</font>

433
00:28:41,070 --> 00:28:43,330
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">ho sopportato.</font>

434
00:28:44,990 --> 00:28:51,830
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">È stato tutto in virtù di questo giorno... 
In virtù di poterti uccidere!</font>

435
00:28:58,840 --> 00:29:02,640
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Io, colui che veniva chiamato Captain Kuro,</font>

436
00:29:02,970 --> 00:29:06,930
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">ho dovuto servire sorridente una ragazzina!</font>

437
00:29:07,850 --> 00:29:12,060
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Anche se non volevo, dovevo ingraziarmi te!</font>

438
00:29:16,900 --> 00:29:18,490
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Bastardo...!</font>

439
00:29:19,070 --> 00:29:22,450
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Capisci l'umiliazione di quei giorni?</font>

440
00:29:23,370 --> 00:29:28,160
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Lo capisci?! Io, che una volta ero chiamato Captain Kuro!</font>

441
00:29:35,550 --> 00:29:38,590
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Kuro!</font>

442
00:29:44,260 --> 00:29:46,640
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Ora che ci penso, con te...</font>

443
00:29:48,980 --> 00:29:52,310
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">con te ho un conto sospeso per avermi colpito.</font>

444
00:29:52,850 --> 00:29:54,520
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Usopp...!</font>

445
00:29:54,860 --> 00:29:59,320
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">In quel momento mi hai 
colpito con tutta la tua forza.</font>

446
00:30:22,550 --> 00:30:27,390
<font face="Impress BT Pace" size="82">Se odi così tanto essere colpito, ti colpirò altre cento volte!</font>

